{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"788b5d689d","title":"中共中央转发云南省委关于禁止村政权经费浪费的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec33a0dfaf","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"788b5d689d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f253a6d15d","type":"title","text":"中共中央转发云南省委关于禁止村政权经费浪费的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"b1e6ea5d84","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局、分局，并转各省委、区党委、直属市委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"278e2662cd","type":"paragraph","text":"村经费支用浪费是一极严重现象，云南省委发了严禁指示，西南局已通知所属遵行。望各地检查此事，按照情况采行为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"521c378cf0","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央五月十四日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"494266a837","type":"subtitle","text":"云南省委禁止村政权浪费指示","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"f8906af297","type":"appellation","text":"各地并报中央：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"e8238c2bd4","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将云南省委关于禁止村级浪费的指示，转发你们，望注意检查有无同类的现象","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"c96649835b","type":"paragraph","text":" 西南局五月四日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"75cf348686","type":"appellation","text":"各地委、工委并西南局：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"a43f4df5a7","type":"paragraph","text":"近来发现各地村经费开支惊人的浪费现象，如以办公为名，吃喝招待，起伙吃大锅饭，甚至招待工作人员看戏、洗澡等，任意挥霍，极大地加重群众负担。此种现象必须立即严禁。兹规定：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"1e54097514","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）各专区即根据村庄大小，规定村脱离生产人数及村办公费，未经批准，不得自行增加。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"7e28008c44","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）工作人员下乡，自带粮草票、菜金，一律不准接受招待。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"d6c18cf538","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）村里不准自筹经费。违背以上规定者，予以处分。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"2067d9cf42","type":"paragraph","text":"接受招待者，以伙同贪污论处。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"9ca5d6394a","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）省府、军区禁止乡村自筹经费，禁止浪费招待的布告，即日拟就发下。各专署即自行翻印，在各地带张贴。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"},{"id":"2dcaf72142","type":"paragraph","text":" 云南省委四月二十八日","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d"}],"page":{"id":"ad2e5cfcb9","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"788b5d689d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}